<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA70">
<l>emakkituvō pērācai yeṉṟun tavirā</l>
<l>temakkorunāḷ kāṭṭutiyō ventā - yamaikkavē</l>
<l>pōnteripāyn taṉṉa puricaṭaiyāy poṅkiravi</l>
<l>lēnteripāyn tāṭu miṭam</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>As for this, it is our great longing, without ever relinquishing:</l>
<l>will you one day show [it] to us, o our father, the place</l>
<l>where you dance spreading emminent flames in the boiling night,</l>
<l>you with matted hair made as if flames spread, come to make an effect.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
